        <link>https://www.tina4.com/documentation/doku.php?id=tina4:tutorials:create-migration&amp;rev=1622183456&amp;do=diff</link>
        <description>How do I create a Table/Migration with Tina4

Connect a Database to your project before attempting this section

Migrations in Tina4 are very easy to do. 

1. Start up your project with 
  composer start
or 
  php -S localhost:7145 index.php 
Run one of these commands from inside the project directory where index.php is located, or it won't work.</description>
